{
  "stem": "21310.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he said my father should have a lot of rest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He had some chest pain, and we didn't know if it was a light heart attack or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But anyway, he did leave-- and in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And as these-- all these thousands of men were leaving, the German airplanes came swoop down very low and started to machine gun these people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we heard the planes, and we heard the noise, and you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then some people came running back saying that they are shooting, machine gunning these people because the roads were just clogged.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There were just a few bridges over the Vistula River and a few highways.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So there were thousands of people on there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we had no idea if my father had survived or not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As it turned out-- it's an aside-- he did survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he and two other men got together, put some of their money, and bought a horse and a wagon because they wanted-- were tired carrying their knapsacks.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they were hoping to, you know, ride, go on the wagon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But they didn't know much about horses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it seems that they got a lame horse, and it was half blind.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it was very decrepit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they-- and so they felt sorry for the horse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the beginning, they put their knapsacks on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they felt sorry for the horse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they unhitched the wagon and left it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they knew that the horse couldn't manage by itself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were still-- they were pulling the horse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And wherever they could, they bought some hay or something for it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then it was getting too, too much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So finally they found a farmer who took the horse from them.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
